{"tid":31142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息：梁齊昕正接受精神科治療 出院無期","createTime":"2016-12-09T13:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T18:25:47.000Z","uid":5195,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56afb653fac9d4ebffb10cfa29300ca19d21a2b2","tid":31142,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:21:31.000Z","msg":"傳媒發現梁振英及其妻子梁唐青儀，近日多次在威爾斯親王醫院出現。據知，梁齊昕現時在該院留醫，情況令人關注。消息人士向《香港01》透露，梁齊昕現時由精神科專科醫生照顧，並在主座暨創傷中心大樓6樓私家病房留醫。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》及《頭條日報》亦分別引述消息指，齊昕早於10月7日已入住威院，至今已留院兩個月。報道又指，梁齊昕精神狀況令人憂慮，其病歷報告被列為「機密文件」，只有精神科部門主管及主診醫生有權查閱；而齊昕暫時出院無期，須待情緒穩定才可考慮讓她出院。"},{"pid":"007b7de276c6cf0313c62a2c086150ab4ffefa19","tid":31142,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:24:58.000Z","msg":"支共軟禁家屬,人又在支那,雙規還會遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d52884bc51307c25c88c6cb7874b39e544f992","tid":31142,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:25:25.000Z","msg":"睇title仲以為9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係就開香檳了"},{"pid":"531f3c1d3e2bca00de6dca937d3fa9f48bd00bc8","tid":31142,"uid":1900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:26:00.000Z","msg":"種善因得善果   相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家報左落自己屋企人到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477e5d63b9d418d4acbb0a8aa94337628d55f670","tid":31142,"uid":44933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:29:39.000Z","msg":"我覺得係做戲<br />\n等佢有下台階唔連任"},{"pid":"42f8616a732ed1cdecc6a38f7bbb18b9499292d8","tid":31142,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:31:06.000Z","msg":"特工落毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cef317782f80486e910cf62e15801aaaeea3a1d","tid":31142,"uid":36901